- namespace name="defs" defs.plim
---!
    class CLS:
        appcontainer = "flex flex-col flex-center bg-yellow-lunar bg-opacity-30 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg min-w-[250px] hover:shadow-2xl transition"

doctype html
html lang="en"
    head
        - call title="Clop - Clipboard optimizer for images" domain="lowtechguys.com" description="Clipboard optimizer for images. Copy large, paste small, send fast" short_description="Clipboard optimizer for images. Copy large, paste small, send fast" favicon="/clop/favicon.ico" icon="clop-icon" icon_size="1280" screenshot="clop-screenshot" color="rgb(212, 212, 216)" defs:head

    body.bg-zinc-300.text-center.max-w-[100vw].flex.flex-col.items-center.min-h-[100vh].justify-between.overflow-x-hidden
        header.flex.items-center.justify-between.px-4.md:px-8.max-w-[100vw].w-[100vw].h-24.text-gray-500.justify-self-end
            a.flex.flex-center.${'hover:transform'}.${'hover:scale-110'} href="/"
                icon.w-16.h-16.md:w-20.md:h-20.filter.drop-shadow-lg.text-zinc-600 : lowtech
            .links
                a.text-sm.md:text-base.ml-4.hidden.md:inline href="/" Other apps
                a.text-sm.md:text-base.ml-4 href="/clop/privacy" Privacy
                a.text-sm.md:text-base.ml-4 href="/contact?app=Clop" Contact

        section#hero.min-w-[100vw].flex-center.flex-col.relative.pb-20
            img.w-28.h-28.md:w-32.md:h-32.filter.drop-shadow-2xl src="/static/img/clop-icon.png"
            h1.mb-6.text-4xl.text-zinc-600 Clop
            h5.text-gray-500.m-0.p-0 Clipboard optimizer for images
            h5.text-gray-500.m-0.p-0.-mt-1 Copy large, paste small, send fast

            .flex.flex-center.mt-8
                a.mr-4.btn.text-white.bg-zinc-700.${'hover:text-black'}.${'hover:bg-zinc-500'}.rounded-lg.flex.justify-center.items-center href="https://files.lowtechguys.com/Clop.zip"
                    icon.h-4.w-4.md:h-7.md:w-7 : package
                    span.ml-2.text-sm.md:text-base Download
                a.btn.text-white.bg-gray-900.${'hover:text-black'}.${'hover:bg-gray-300'}.flex.justify-center.items-center href="https://github.com/alin23/Clop"
                    icon.h-4.w-4.md:h-7.md:w-7 : github
                    span.ml-2.text-sm.md:text-base View Source
            .text-red-700.text-xxs.mt-4.font-medium.opacity-50
                | compatible with macOS `b 13.0+` (Ventura and later)

        section#details.flex-center.flex-col.pb-20.space-y-24.px-8
            .flex.flex-col.space-y-2.md:w-2/3.text-left
                h1.text-3xl.text-center.md:text-left.lg:text-4xl.mb-1.text-gray-800 Optimize images as soon as you copy them
                .text-base.lg:text-lg.text-gray-600
                    As long as the Clop app is running, every time you copy an image to your `b clipboard`, Clop will `b optimize` it to the `b smallest possible size`.
                .text-base.lg:text-lg.text-gray-600
                    -md
                        Clop uses the following utilities for optimizing different kinds of images:

                        * `pngquant` for PNG
                        * `jpegoptim` for JPEG
                        * `gifsicle` for GIF
            .flex.flex-col.space-y-2.md:w-2/3.text-left
                h1.text-3xl.text-center.md:text-left.lg:text-4xl.mb-1.text-gray-800 What's up with the hat in the icon?
                .text-base.lg:text-lg.text-gray-600
                    -md
                        *Clop* is the Romanian word for a traditional straw hat with a high crown and raised conical brim, worn more as an adorment in days of celebration.

                        We thought *"**Cl**ipboard **Op**timizer"* sounds a bit too technical and doesn't roll off the tongue as easily. We're <b class="text-red-hot">Rom</b><b class="text-amber-500">an</b><b class="text-blue-500">ian</b> ourselves and we thought it might be a good idea to keep the memory of our traditions from dying completely, with whatever little we can do.


        footer.flex.items-center.justify-between.px-2.md:px-8.max-w-[100vw].w-[100vw].h-24.text-gray-500.justify-self-end
            h4.font-extralight.text-gray-500.hidden.md:block The low-tech guys Â© 2022
            .links.w-full.md:w-auto
                / a.text-red-hot.ml-4 href="/contact" Contact
        -stylus
            @import "stylus/base"

            em
                color var(--color-orange-800)
            strong
                color var(--color-red-700)
            li
                margin-bottom 4px

            #faq
                code
                    background-color alpha(blue, 0.25)
                    color var(--color-gray-700)
                    padding 0 .5rem

                h2
                    padding 0.1rem 0.5rem
                    border-radius 0.5rem

                p
                    padding 0.1rem 0.5rem
                    color var(--color-gray-700)

                hr
                    border-color alpha(blue, 0.1)
                li
                    line-height 1.8

            a
                color var(--color-blue-400)
            .links
                a
                    background-color alpha(black, 0.1)
                    color black
